spec_data.Name: python2-baker
spec_data.Description:
Baker lets you easily add a command line interface to your Python functions
using a simple decorator, to create scripts with "sub-commands", similar to
Django's 'manage.py', 'svn', 'hg', etc.

Python 2 version.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 11:54:49 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Easy, powerful access to Python functions from the command line
